main event: A correspondence related to a panel discussion on UFOs hosted by the American Society of Newspaper Editors in April 1967.
interesting points: Major Hector Quintanilla, Jr. gave an official presentation to the American Society of Newspaper Editors on April 22, 1967., The document includes a letter of appreciation to Major Quintanilla from Newbold Noyes, Jr. for participating in the event., The Air Force planned to have Major Quintanilla appear at a panel discussion with prominent scientists and skeptics regarding UFOs., The letters reflect a significant interest from the media in UFOs during the 1960s., The American Society of Newspaper Editors consisted of around 700 newspaper editors, indicating the discussion's importance.
